<item>
            <title>[LU-9088] use od_is_ost check OST FID</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9088</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From Wangdi:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Because OST FLDB is not created until 2.6, so&lt;br/&gt;
if the DNE system is upgraded from 2.5 to &amp;gt;=&lt;br/&gt;
2.6, then the local FLDB will not be loaded&lt;br/&gt;
in fld_index_init(), which might cause OSD&lt;br/&gt;
can not tell OST FID created by 2.5. So let&apos;s&lt;br/&gt;
use od_is_ost in this case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
